| Folder | Reason Dead |
|--------|-------------|
| `E:\KLIPAURA_MASTER_AUTOMATION\` | Empty skeleton, never populated |
| `E:\KLIPAURA-old-full-backup\` | Snapshot superseded by current system |
| `E:\KLIPAURA BACKUP\` | Snapshot superseded by current system |
| `E:\ARCHIVE_AND_LEGACY\` | n8n workflows and legacy scripts, all replaced |
