## ACTIVE WORKSPACE

All new code lives in `E:\KLIPAURA\`. If a file path starts with anything other than `E:\KLIPAURA\` you are working in the wrong place.

## N8N — PERMANENTLY REMOVED

There are no n8n workflows in KLIPAURA. If you find yourself writing a workflow JSON file or referencing n8n APIs, stop. All orchestration is Python-native workers and the `schedule` library.
